options.label: Minimalist
options.results_text: Your tastes are refined and your interests highbrow, to the point that other people might consider you a bit intimidating, but you never let that stop you from being yourself. You see the beauty in restraint and practicality, and you deserve a cake that you can proudly display as a centrepiece at your (undoubtedly classy) bash.

options.label: Classic
options.results_text: You may be level-headed and uncomplicated, but deep down you’ve never really let go of your inner child, and you’re an easy, positive person to be around because of it. Your carefree nature makes most people instantly want to be your new BFF. You’ll doubtless be spending your birthday in an intimate gathering with your favourite people, and what better for the occasion than a cake that’s as playful and unaffected as you are?

options.label: Abstract
options.results_text: You march to the beat of your own drum and would hate, above all else, to be labelled “normal”. You love trying new things and typically have a countless number of passion projects on the go. Your friends would struggle to describe your personality with just a few words—there’s just too much going on there! The only cake for you is one that’s as one-of-a-kind as you are.

options.label: The works
options.results_text: You’ve never understood the adage that says “moderation is best in all things”; if something makes you happy, you want as much of it as you can get! You’d rather life be complicated than boring, which isn’t to say you’re a raging party animal; in fact, your ideal night could best be described as “cozy”. You need a cake that’s as warm, inviting and full of happiness as you are!

options.label: Maximalist
options.results_text: You tend to have a lot going on at all times, but even when it seems like you’ve bitten off more than you can chew, you somehow always make it work; you love having fun way too much to let the little things get you down. You’re in the unique position of being both the life of the party and the parent of your friend group, and you need a cake that’s as wild as you are, and brimming with as much positivity!

options.label: Floral
options.results_text: Underneath a delicate, gentle facçade lies a bold spirit. A true romantic at heart, you don’t only see yourself as the protagonist of your own life, but as the protagonist of an epic modern-day fairytale. You deserve a cake fit for royalty, and which is, like you, equal parts sweet and fierce.

You’d rather life be complicated than boring, which isn’t to say you’re a raging party animal; in fact, your ideal night could best be described as “cozy”. You need a cake that’s as warm, inviting and full of happiness as you are!

options.label: Maximalist
options.results_text: You tend to have a lot going on at all times, but even when it seems like you’ve bitten off more than you can chew, you somehow always make it work; you love having fun way too much to let the little things get you down. You’re in the unique position of being both the life of the party and the parent of your friend group, and you need a cake that’s as wild as you are, and brimming with as much positivity!

options.label: Floral
options.results_text: Underneath a delicate, gentle facçade lies a bold spirit. A true romantic at heart, you don’t only see yourself as the protagonist of your own life, but as the protagonist of an epic modern-day fairytale. You deserve a cake fit for royalty, and which is, like you, equal parts sweet and fierce.
